<p>Raila Odinga, former Kenyan prime minister and the country’s longtime opposition leader, died in India on Wednesday at age 80 while receiving medical treatment [bbc.com#1][nytimes.com#1][aljazeera.com#1][dw.com#1]. Hospital and media reports in Kerala said he collapsed during a morning walk and suffered a heart attack/cardiac arrest; he was taken to Devamatha Hospital where his death was confirmed [abcnews.go.com#2][ndtv.com#1][scmp.com#1][thehindu.com#1]. Odinga ran for Kenya’s presidency five times and is widely credited with helping usher in multiparty democracy after the one‑party era, including a period of imprisonment during that struggle [nytimes.com#1][dw.com#1][lemonde.fr#1][straitstimes.com#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/q53w7vVmFesMXS9YVGzaU2jHW_ZsxR2nEsBe1cJtSPORglPGRu2YPxOHYQ_OYpryQNX_BXu2qzP_LD2jGXurezQSAbv1bKw6_TLhVwLdbsmN-Wkaku-RmUnrdfdXa9nblaBO6iWYjl2VwXaowggZgqOZ1225QKSZL7sDV6rbNYxV5bca9UGEFA' alt='Raila Odinga, a former prime minister of Kenya, in 2022.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Circumstances noted: Odinga collapsed during a morning walk in Kerala and suffered a heart attack/cardiac arrest; he was pronounced dead at Devamatha Hospital on Wednesday [ndtv.com#1][abcnews.go.com#2][scmp.com#1][bbc.com#1].</li><li>Medical visit: He was in India receiving medical treatment at the time of his death [bbc.com#1][aljazeera.com#1].</li><li>Political legacy: He ran for Kenya’s presidency five times and was seen as pivotal in advancing multiparty democracy [nytimes.com#1][lemonde.fr#1][dw.com#1].</li><li>Years of sacrifice: Odinga was imprisoned while opposing Kenya’s former one‑party autocracy before entering parliament [straitstimes.com#1][lemonde.fr#1].</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Devamatha Hospital (Kerala): Hospital officials stated he suffered a cardiac arrest after collapsing during a morning walk and confirmed his death. (<a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/africa/article/3329120/raila-odinga-ex-kenyan-pm-and-democracy-fighter-dies-80-after-heart-attack-india'>South China Morning Post</a>)</li><li>DW analysis: He is remembered for his key role in Kenya&#x27;s democratic journey over more than three decades. (<a href='https://www.dw.com/en/kenya-s-opposition-giant-raila-odinga-dies-aged-80/a-74364791'>DW</a>)</li><li>Raila Odinga’s stance (past claims): He maintained he was cheated of victory in several presidential contests. (<a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/le-monde-africa/article/2025/10/15/former-kenyan-prime-minister-raila-odinga-dies-at-80_6746450_124.html'>Le Monde</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2025/oct/15/raila-odinga-former-kenya-pm-dies'>Raila Odinga, key Kenyan opposition figure and former PM, dies aged 80</a> - theguardian.com</li><li><a href='https://www.dw.com/en/kenya-s-opposition-giant-raila-odinga-dies-aged-80/a-74364791'>Kenya&#x27;s opposition giant Raila Odinga dies aged 80</a> - dw.com</li><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/former-kenya-pm-raila-odinga-dies-of-heart-attack-in-kerala-9458146#publisher=newsstand'>Former Kenya PM Raila Odinga Dies Of Heart Attack In Kerala</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/le-monde-africa/article/2025/10/15/former-kenyan-prime-minister-raila-odinga-dies-at-80_6746450_124.html'>Kenyan opposition leader Raila Odinga dies at 80</a> - lemonde.fr</li><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/africa/article/3329120/raila-odinga-ex-kenyan-pm-and-democracy-fighter-dies-80-after-heart-attack-india'>Former Kenyan PM Odinga dies in India at 80</a> - scmp.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c1m39xg4dggo'>Former Kenyan Prime Minister Raila Odinga dies in India aged 80</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/former-kenyan-premier-raila-odinga-key-figure-african-126536436'>Former Kenyan premier Raila Odinga, a key figure in African politics, dies at 80</a> - abcnews.go.com</li><li><a href='h